data.description: Welcome to 9755 Mason Ln, a charming Cape Cod in Fairdale, KY. Enjoy the peacefulness of a large backyard and a pond just outside the fenced-in area. This home is a perfect combination of warmth and convenience, with a spacious living room, two first-floor bedrooms, a cozy dining room located off the kitchen, and first-floor laundry. Ascend the stairs to the third bedroom, located on the second floor of the home. This home offers plenty of living space for any size family. The large storage shed provides additional space for any outdoor items or tools. All of this and more, at an unbeatable price of $260,000. With its age and character, this lovely home is an excellent opportunity to create a custom space to call your own. Don't miss out on this great opportunity!
